# Some things that still need to be done

- support building as a shared object library
- optionally INSPECTOR should output as JSON
- Solaris 11 support: get address & MTU ioctls; byte swap; sync; SPIN_MASK
- support DNS lookups on addresses passed as arguments to programs
- rewrite pubmux & submux as C programs, and document them
- develop a Common Lisp foreign function interface
- develop Java, Python and Go interfaces without proprietary code
- develop simpler READER & WRITER example programs using the batch functions
